The residual vs fitted values plot does not give a clear trend so we conclude that the equal variance assumption is also satisfied.

2(b) Age is covariate

# test if major affects covariate
model.2.1 = lm(Age ~ Major,data=data2)

To assess model assumptions, we have a look at QQ Plot for normality and residual vs fitted values plot for equal variance assumptions. The points on QQ Plot appear to be close to the straight line except one point of bottom left corner, we would say normality assumption is roughly satisfied. The residual vs fitted values plot does not give a clear trend so we conclude that the equal variance assumption is also satisfied. Assumptions looks good.
